node.text:
Meet your 2021 Artist for Social Change, Meagan De Lima @meagandelima 

Single: You Can 

“This program made me realize the power and value art holds. Within the program, there were so many meaningful experiences...” said De Lima 

learn more about @meagandelima journey and advice by visiting artshelp.net/meagandelima / link in bio 

Artists for Social Change is an interactive arts education program and showcase offering workshops and accessible resources to artists!

This program is created by remarkable partners @remingtonbuilds and @consciouseconomics supported by @redcrosscanada @esdc.edsc with amazing community partners @nwye.co @queer.collective @thehoneyjam @op.pfc and emerging artists program partner @rbcxmusic
